{"tid":1946553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[入嚟睇回信] 我幾個月前開始喺隻同陌生人交換短信嘅樹窿game分享香港革命","createTime":"2020-03-27T16:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T18:31:37.000Z","uid":168267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64d89fab587d079b8d143866bdf79efbb1261b82","tid":1946553,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"首先，希望大家唔好笑我軟弱，搵樹窿搵到去Steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想將負能量射畀其他同路人，所以一見到Steam有隻專門用嚟匿名寄信、收信，畀用戶做分享嘅「game」，就買咗番嚟，用《乾柴烈火》入面奶共嬅對住水樽傾訴心事之後倒啲水落街嘅心態開始呻<br />\n<br />\nKind Words<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1070710/Kind_Words_lo_fi_chill_beats_to_write_to/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1070710%2FKind_Words_lo_fi_chill_beats_to_write_to%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=853dc32a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1070710/Kind_Words_lo_fi_chill_beats_to_write_to/</a><br />\n<br />\n隻game淨係得寫信同收信，過程完全匿名，另外仲有啲stamp之類嘅collectibles<br />\n信有行數限制，可以寫嘅嘢唔多，玩家既可以做呻嗰個，亦可以選擇回信畀其他呻嘅人<br />\n網絡世界好多人都又濕鳩又口臭，國難當前仲要面子行先，日日嗌唔停口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲事見得多，士氣受打擊在所難免，希望大家睇完可以補充番啲正能量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYYb4Fq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYYb4Fq.jpg&h=1bbb9678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tHsC0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tHsC0q.jpg&h=73c31f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9crw4Fr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9crw4Fr.jpg&h=de8a2f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQrMTyN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQrMTyN.jpg&h=12e90452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXNPRks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXNPRks.jpg&h=0fc31398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05h8nr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05h8nr8.jpg&h=1f9a89a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Adc8nr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdc8nr8.jpg&h=cd74916e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMMTyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMMTyP.jpg&h=56049fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4rAMTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4rAMTQ.jpg&h=c8aafdfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EiH4FdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEiH4FdR.jpg&h=32365796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rppKFdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrppKFdT.jpg&h=762ffa98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTbhfNe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTbhfNe.jpg&h=f2fc965b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6XcO7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6XcO7f.jpg&h=0921fd99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享完畢<br />\n希望大家都唔好放棄<br />\n我哋冇分化同放棄嘅本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW我最鐘意呢個：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQTjt7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQTjt7T.jpg&h=9bf9bc78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4bf72e463740095aebfe5be62d4ecf1bea957d","tid":1946553,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"